est of the group if we are tanking.  So yes a well played SK can tank just not Vindi.<br><br>But again, I'm sorry I even posted here knowing how different our views of the SK Class and HP's are.<br><br>Neptunis<br>&nbsp;<br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 56 DE Revenant</td></tr>
