	   <tr><td colspan=2>Sounds like a good plan as long as the area isn't 1 where the feared 1 will find more adds on it's way back.&nbsp;&nbsp;You have a nice area for it there, just watch that whenever you try this in a new zone or camp.<br><br>Also, you don't need to wait at all after you fear.  Once fear goes off immediately FD, the feared one will still run but the other's won't follow.  This prevents any chance of interuptions from MOBs if you do it quick enough, and if it fails your just back where you started, not down a bubble of life waiting for the icon to refresh.<br><br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 55 DE Revenant<br>&nbsp;<br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 56 DE Revenant</td></tr>
