	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well I'm not sure your Server so it effects what you can afford a little but I'll give a few solid choices.<br><br>First I think the Ornate Runed Blade is a tremendous and under-rated weapon.&nbsp;&nbsp;At 19/30 with +3 to all resists it's a real meat grinder, but won't give you increadably high hits, just alot of above average ones, sells for about 500pp.<br><br>The Blade of Xelgoz is another really great choice for it's +STR and high damage.  I can't quote stats for it right now but damage is over 20 with a ratio better than 1:2, sells for about 500pp.<br><br>The Thoneblade Yakesha is another hard hitting 2hs which is now selling for below 1k most places.<br><br>I think what most people are looking for now is the 30/40, 30/39 or so Velious 2hs weapons, which sell for about 5k still on my server.  So I'd recommend that if you have 2hb skill get a Deathbringer Rod 30/40 2hb SK only, since they now sell for about 1k.<br><br>One other choice &quot;Strength of Gorodan&quot;  41/51 2hs +25 STR wt 1.5 NO DROP.  Drops in Maiden's Eye as an uncommon drop.  If you can get there a solid group of about lvl 50 can kill the Umbrus whatever (martians) that drop them.  It will give you those really high hits, but you'll want Haste when using it.<br><br>But you got some ideas now, I know there are more but these are all ones I have used.  Good luck.<br><br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 55 DE Revenant<br>&nbsp;<br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 56 DE Revenant</td></tr>
